#

Sizzling Beef and Broccoli Stir-Fry

$15.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten-Free

Tags:

AsianStir-FryQuick Meal

Description

A quick and delicious stir-fry featuring tender beef and vibrant broccoli, tossed in a savory sauce.

Ingredients

  • Beef Sirloin: 1 lb, thinly sliced
  • Broccoli Florets: 2 cups
  • Soy Sauce: 1/4 cup
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Ginger: 1 inch, grated
  • Sesame Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Cornstarch: 1 tbsp
  • Vegetable Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Green Onions: 2, chopped for garnish
